<lb n="0239a18"/><head type="no">No. 610</head>
<lb n="0239a19"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><title><note n="0239002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0239002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛說〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0239002"><lem>佛說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>內身觀章句<note n="0239003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＋（一卷）【宮】</note><app n="0239003"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">經一卷</rdg></app></title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0239a20"/>
<lb n="0239a21"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0239004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">失譯…漢錄＝漢失譯【宋】【元】【宮】，漢失譯師名【明】</note><note n="0239004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">失譯…漢錄＝漢失譯【宋】【元】【宮】，＝漢失譯師名【明】</note><app n="0239004" word-count="8"><lem>失譯人名在後漢錄</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">漢失譯</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">漢失譯師名</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0239a22"/><div1 type="jing"><lg><l>一切一其心</l><l>皆聽美言訓</l>
<lb n="0239a23"/><l>佛所<note n="0239005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">從＝行【宮】</note><app n="0239005"><lem>從</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">行</rdg></app>得道</l><l>且聽我彼經</l>
<lb n="0239a24"/><l>彼空亦不斷</l><l>有行皆非常</l>
<lb n="0239a25"/><l>夫行不敗壞</l><l>佛以講授經</l>
<lb n="0239a26"/><l>深微難見事</l><l>非章原之句</l>
<lb n="0239a27"/><l>通彼能敷演</l><l>是以故為師</l>
<lb n="0239a28"/><l>從本以存本</l><l>有造法之積</l>
<lb n="0239a29"/><l>從慧以除棄</l><l>上士所講說</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T15.0610.0239b" n="0239b"/>
<lb n="0239b01"/><l>所從因緣有</l><l>有行皆無有</l>
<lb n="0239b02"/><l>亦有前世<note n="0239006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">除＝除【元】【明】</note><app n="0239006"><lem>除</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho"><todo/>除</rdg></app></l><l>無知彼諸行</l>
<lb n="0239b03"/><l>亦如欲演身</l><l>日親之所講</l>
<lb n="0239b04"/><l><note n="0239007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＝夫【三】，大災＝夫裁【宮】</note><note n="0239007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大災＝夫裁【宮】，大＝夫【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0239007"><lem>大災</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">夫裁</rdg><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">夫災</rdg></app>患無數</l><l>皆以歸流身</l>
<lb n="0239b05"/><l>刪定如本文</l><l>所演眾要言</l>
<lb n="0239b06"/><l>靡麗五字句</l><l>明誓以勸勉</l>
<lb n="0239b07"/><l>以頌文具足</l><l>偶字音商備</l>
<lb n="0239b08"/><l>若花實雜<note n="0239008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">糅＝采【宮】</note><app n="0239008"><lem>糅</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">采</rdg></app></l><l>皆聽彼我誨</l>
<lb n="0239b09"/><l>身非人非命</l><l>不丈夫非士</l>
<lb n="0239b10"/><l>若體若<note n="0239009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不＝有【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不＝有【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239009"><lem>不</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">有</rdg></app>&CB00672;</l><l>斯事都無彼</l>
<lb n="0239b11"/><l>夫身造而有</l><l>以有即敗亡</l>
<lb n="0239b12"/><l>無強皆歸<note n="0239010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">命＝終【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">命＝終【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239010"><lem>命</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">終</rdg></app></l><l>如沫蹈踐碎</l>
<lb n="0239b13"/><l>無強則無常</l><l>無常即無樂</l>
<lb n="0239b14"/><l>無常亦為苦</l><l>非身身非我</l>
<lb n="0239b15"/><l>身非常亦苦</l><l>非彼應為身</l>
<lb n="0239b16"/><l><note n="0239011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">若＝苦【宮】</note><app n="0239011"><lem>若</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">苦</rdg></app>體&CB00672;我有</l><l>身都無可有</l>
<lb n="0239b17"/><l>若以都無體</l><l>有存亦有亡</l>
<lb n="0239b18"/><l>慧者以本末</l><l>何彼已有體</l>
<lb n="0239b19"/><l>若以無<note n="0239012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">主＝生【宮】</note><app n="0239012"><lem>主</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">生</rdg></app>者</l><l>不得以自由</l>
<lb n="0239b20"/><l>有校計若此</l><l>何彼體我有</l>
<lb n="0239b21"/><l>斯體身為空</l><l>體我有為虛</l>
<lb n="0239b22"/><l>應因緣為有</l><l>非身逝心造</l>
<lb n="0239b23"/><l>非眾人身造</l><l>亦非自身造</l>
<lb n="0239b24"/><l>都無<note n="0239013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">身有＝有身【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">身有＝有身【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239013"><lem>身有</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">有身</rdg></app>造</l><l>亦身<note n="0239014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無不＝不無【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無不＝不無【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239014"><lem>無不</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">不無</rdg></app>造</l>
<lb n="0239b25"/><l>以身無造者</l><l>從彼為得諦</l>
<lb n="0239b26"/><l>亦非都骨節</l>
<lb n="0239b27"/><l>從前世方來</l><l>亦非天造身</l>
<lb n="0239b28"/><l>非神所化<note n="0239015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">城＝成【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">城＝成【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239015"><lem>城</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">成</rdg></app></l><l>非無行無本</l>
<lb n="0239b29"/><l>無因為自有</l><l>是身有所由</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T15.0610.0239c" n="0239c"/>
<lb n="0239c01"/><l>有事亦有<note n="0239016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">物＝初【宮】</note><app n="0239016"><lem>物</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">初</rdg></app></l><l>有本有所起</l>
<lb n="0239c02"/><l>稍稍為生有</l><l>本以癡亦愛</l>
<lb n="0239c03"/><l>心與愛有漏</l><l>亦有縛亦結</l>
<lb n="0239c04"/><l>行二品為漏</l><l>斯為本亦餘</l>
<lb n="0239c05"/><l>世與受因緣</l><l>以由彼斯身</l>
<lb n="0239c06"/><l>以漸能致有</l><l>初<note n="0239017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">始＝如【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">始＝如【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239017"><lem>始</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">如</rdg></app>有精沫</l>
<lb n="0239c07"/><l>精沫為轉凝</l><l>足為生<note n="0239018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">兩＝雨【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0239018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">兩＝雨【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0239018"><lem>兩</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">雨</rdg></app><app type="＊" source="0239018"><lem>兩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">雨</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0239c08"/><l>以<app type="＊" source="0239018"><lem>兩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">雨</rdg></app>為轉厚</l><l>以序有四體</l>
<lb n="0239c09"/><l>為生頭第五</l><l>若干骨積聚</l>
<lb n="0239c10"/><l>從行為用成</l><l>頭九為髑髏</l>
<lb n="0239c11"/><l>頞&CB02929;為二骨</l><l>齒根三十二</l>
<lb n="0239c12"/><l>齒三十二骨</l><l>頸為與<note n="0239019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耳＝身【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耳＝身【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239019"><lem>耳</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">身</rdg></app>本</l>
<lb n="0239c13"/><l>鼻為與上&CB00171;</l><l>心與頸嚨喉</l>
<lb n="0239c14"/><l>凡為骨<note n="0239020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">八十＝十八【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">八十＝十八【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239020"><lem>八十</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">十八</rdg></app></l><l>頰車與頸四</l>
<lb n="0239c15"/><l>咽亦為骨四</l><l>左臂與右臂</l>
<lb n="0239c16"/><l>凡有骨五十</l><l>若其斯左&CB00169;</l>
<lb n="0239c17"/><l>應有十三肋</l><l>亦斯右&CB00169;然</l>
<lb n="0239c18"/><l>應有肋十三</l><l>斯為四十八</l>
<lb n="0239c19"/><l>三三三相連</l><l>二為二相連</l>
<lb n="0239c20"/><l>其餘不相連</l><l>身者以為<note n="0239021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">彊＝疆【明】＊</note><note n="0239021" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="＊"/>彊＝疆【明】＊</note><app n="0239021"><lem>彊</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">疆</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0239c21"/><l>如束葦無彊</l><l>脊膂三十二</l>
<lb n="0239c22"/><l>尻與腰為三</l><l>若其斯左脾</l>
<lb n="0239c23"/><l>骨為二十五</l><l>右髀為亦然</l>
<lb n="0239c24"/><l>為骨二十五</l><l>肩<note n="0239022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">髀＝　【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">髀＝&lac-space;【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>髀有骨四</l>
<lb n="0239c25"/><l>凡三百二十</l><l>敷演<note n="0239023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">名＝各【宮】</note><app n="0239023"><lem>名</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">各</rdg></app>之諦</l>
<lb n="0239c26"/><l>佛以日斷嗣</l><l>彼&CB00556;悉以聚</l>
<lb n="0239c27"/><l>諸根<note n="0239024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">為以＝以為【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">為以＝以為【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239024"><lem>為以</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">以為</rdg></app>縫</l><l>非瘡而裹之</l>
<lb n="0239c28"/><l>肉血以塗<note n="0239025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB02949;＝身【三】【宮】</note><note n="0239025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB02949;＝身【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0239025"><lem>&CB02949;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">身</rdg></app></l><l>如木機關縷</l>
<lb n="0239c29"/><l>為如幻師幻</l><l>骨機關亦然</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T15.0610.0240a" n="0240a"/>
<lb n="0240a01"/><l>以筋纏縛成</l><l>合聚骨若此</l>
<lb n="0240a02"/><l>以為是形體</l><l>愚者莫不著</l>
<lb n="0240a03"/><l>智者而不著</l><l>生革以隱蔽</l>
<lb n="0240a04"/><l>九孔為大瘡</l><l>周匝為滲漏</l>
<lb n="0240a05"/><l>不淨腐臭處</l><l>口啄如為孔</l>
<lb n="0240a06"/><l>滿之以諸穀</l><l>是身為若此</l>
<lb n="0240a07"/><l>以進若干<note n="0240001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">腑＝腐【三】【宮】</note><note n="0240001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">腑＝腐【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0240001"><lem>腑</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">腐</rdg></app></l><l>毛髮與爪齒</l>
<lb n="0240a08"/><l>塵埃亦皮革</l><l>骨節亦骨髓</l>
<lb n="0240a09"/><l>為凡筋與脈</l><l>胃與心亦脾</l>
<lb n="0240a10"/><l>大腸亦小腸</l><l>肝與肺亦腎</l>
<lb n="0240a11"/><l>脂<note n="0240002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB02924;＝&CB00698;【三】【宮】</note><note n="0240002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB02924;＝&CB00698;【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0240002"><lem>&CB02924;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&CB00698;</rdg></app>亦大便</l><l>淚與唾亦<note n="0240003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">汗＝污【三】</note><note n="0240003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">汗＝污【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0240003"><lem>汗</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">污</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0240a12"/><l>鼻涕膏亦血</l><l>寒熱肪小便</l>
<lb n="0240a13"/><l><note n="0240004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB02965;＝腦【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0240004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB02965;＝腦【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0240004"><lem>&CB02965;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">腦</rdg></app>之與<app type="＊" source="0240004"><lem>&CB02965;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">腦</rdg></app>膜</l><l>皆以沈沒彼</l>
<lb n="0240a14"/><l>如泥塗老牛</l><l>如其成不知</l>
<lb n="0240a15"/><l>身之內與外</l><l>夫城骨與牆</l>
<lb n="0240a16"/><l>肉血為塗嚴</l><l>為怨所破壞</l>
<lb n="0240a17"/><l>甯陞H內外</l><l>彼<note n="0240005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">央＝中【三】【宮】</note><note n="0240005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">央＝中【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0240005"><lem>央</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">中</rdg></app>若<note n="0240006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">干＝千【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0240006"><lem>干</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">千</rdg></app>百</l>
<lb n="0240a18"/><l>以為貪其肉</l><l>其外亦災害</l>
<lb n="0240a19"/><l>皆以多尤彼</l><l>斯身腐敗壞</l>
<lb n="0240a20"/><l>譬如久故城</l><l>晝夜供<note n="0240007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">侍＝待【三】【宮】</note><note n="0240007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">侍＝待【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0240007"><lem>侍</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">待</rdg></app>之</l>
<lb n="0240a21"/><l>壞如已復壞</l><l>如坎與空聚</l>
<lb n="0240a22"/><l>痤s賊俱止</l><l>取之欺殆人</l>
<lb n="0240a23"/><l>身為毒虺穴</l><l>夫毒虺劇毒</l>
<lb n="0240a24"/><l>琱_身居止</l><l>喜怒<note n="0240008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">毒＝恚【三】【宮】</note><note n="0240008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">毒＝恚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0240008"><lem>毒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">恚</rdg></app>奸<note n="0240009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">弊＝蔽【三】【宮】</note><note n="0240009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">弊＝蔽【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0240009"><lem>弊</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">蔽</rdg></app></l>
<lb n="0240a25"/><l>孚不和大毒</l><l>正使滿百歲</l>
<lb n="0240a26"/><l>琤H和安隱</l><l>忿則無<note n="0240010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">反＝返【三】【宮】</note><note n="0240010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">反＝返【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0240010"><lem>反</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">返</rdg></app>復</l>
<lb n="0240a27"/><l>須臾<note n="0240011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">復＝頃【宮】</note><app n="0240011"><lem>復</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">頃</rdg></app>不安</l><l>斯身為災禍</l>
<lb n="0240a28"/><l>嫌而有恐畏</l><l>如虎遊荒澤</l>
<lb n="0240a29"/><l>有畏多恐怖</l><l>諸念為以仰</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T15.0610.0240b" n="0240b"/>
<lb n="0240b01"/><l>為一切苦器</l><l>亦為諸劇事</l>
<lb n="0240b02"/><l>斯身主為受</l><l>沈於苦之法</l>
<lb n="0240b03"/><l>一切諸病宅</l><l>為老死之法</l>
<lb n="0240b04"/><l>身為增恩愛</l><l>苦以寒與熱</l>
<lb n="0240b05"/><l>或風而不和</l><l>是則病<note n="0240012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">如＝始【明】</note><app n="0240012"><lem>如</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">始</rdg></app>生</l>
<lb n="0240b06"/><l>為敗壞諸根</l><l><note n="0240013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">失＝夫【元】【明】</note><app n="0240013"><lem>失</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">夫</rdg></app>疾賊害人</l>
<lb n="0240b07"/><l>老死笮厄人</l><l>如雪聚得火</l>
<lb n="0240b08"/><l>疾而為解釋</l><l>斯若此無數</l>
<lb n="0240b09"/><l>身之多災禍</l><l>吾所演一切</l>
<lb n="0240b10"/><l>未能已備具</l><l>要以為諸苦</l>
<lb n="0240b11"/><l>腐身為不實</l><l>多因緣以成</l>
<lb n="0240b12"/><l>大<note n="0240014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耶＝邪【三】【宮】</note><note n="0240014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耶＝邪【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0240014"><lem>耶</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">邪</rdg></app>以為<note n="0240015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">軀＋（十一因緣章…得道疾）百二十四字卷末別出【三】【宮】</note><note n="0240015" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="a"/>軀＋（十一因緣章…得道疾）百二十四字卷末別出【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>軀</l></lg></div1>
<lb n="0240b13"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead><title><app type="＊" source="0239002"><lem>佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>內身觀章句<note n="0240016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＋（一卷）【宋】【宮】</note><app n="0240016"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">經一卷</rdg></app></title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0240b14"/><div1 type="W"><head>十一因緣章</head>
<lb n="0240b15"/><p>佛言。行者有十一因緣。滅道制令<note n="0240017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">人＝入【宋】</note><app n="0240017"><lem>人</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">入</rdg></app>不
<lb n="0240b16"/>墮<note n="0240018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔惡〕－【宮】</note><app n="0240018"><lem>惡</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>道。當不識者。謂萬物。一為大會。謂
<lb n="0240b17"/>人眾。二者多食。謂諸美。亦謂過飽。三者為
<lb n="0240b18"/>多行。謂多業。四為多<note n="0240019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔喧〕－【宮】</note><app n="0240019"><lem>喧</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。謂多語。五為多
<lb n="0240b19"/>睡眠。六為會聚。謂禪中。七為習行。謂多事。
<lb n="0240b20"/>八為愛身。九為輕。謂非法語。十為貪謂多
<lb n="0240b21"/>欲。十一為不好善處居。謂惡人中。行道者
<lb n="0240b22"/>當斷是十一因緣。得道疾。</p></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>